name: CIBC Core Fixed Income Pool
longDescription: This ETF will focus on generating regular income, with a secondary focus on generating modest long-term capital appreciation, by investing primarily in units of other mutual funds that invest in fixed income securities. The fund invests primarily in units of other mutual funds that invest in fixed income securities.
